description: Adam’s Grub Truck is an up and coming new addition to the booming world of mobile eateries. Living in such an eclectic and vibrant area we are surrounded by a diverse community of traditional and contemporary range of food options.Adam’s Grub Truck offers sandwiches with uniquely blended traditional Asian flavors with a contemporary twist of good old American comfort food to give each sandwich a personalized touch.We will provide fresh, fast, unique and innovative food creations fit for any appetite. Our concept is simple...more bang for your buck! Nothing but the highest standards in quality, service and value.
name: Adam's Grub Truck
